Option Set: ASICS Gel Sensei 4 Men's Shoes
Product Description: You'll feel like more than just a pupil in the Asics Gel Sensei 4's.  These shoes are the masters of stability and comfort on court, and your feet will agree when you step out of the dojo.  Asics' legendary gel-cushioning system gives this shoe a plush ride; combine that with the Biomorphic fit, and you'll never want to take these bad boys off.  The shoe fits like a glove thanks to the asymmetrical lacing system, and it also provides plenty of support since it's been outfitted with A-Truss technology, which helps your rear to forefoot transitioning as well as acting like a rearfoot stabilizer.  The tongue and upper of the shoe are lined with a thin cushioning layer underneath a screen of mesh, giving this shoe ample breathability.  If you're a strong, aggressive mover on court, you should definitely have a look at this shoe; the Sensei will never lead you astray. Fit: Length fit is standard.
